# Rules
- Always analyze codebase first and familiarize yourself with project structure.

## Tools
We will only use Bun (never npm) for this project.
We will only use Astro for this project. (https://docs.astro.build/en/getting-started/)
We will use Tailwind and Css for this project.

Refer to their documentation for information on how to use them and best practices.
Always check your solution with the documentation and best practices.

Do not make up factual information. Do not hallucinate.

